item.title: Ep.219 - Aviation furniture with Stu Art
item.description:
In this episode, we look at how aviation and aerospace items are converted to art and furniture pieces, and we welcome Stuart Abbot, the founder of Stu Art Furniture. 

Stuart trained as an Airframe Engineer in the RAF working on the Tornado F3. After leaving the RAF he continued as an airframe engineer with several international airlines and started Stu Art Furniture in 2012... Feed: https://anchor.fm/s/993e5154/podcast/rss
